Revision history for App-grindperl

0.004     2015-12-09 14:52:03-05:00 America/New_York

    [ADDED]

    - Added the '-A' flag for Configure

0.003     2015-02-22 06:56:11-05:00 America/New_York

    [DOCS]

    - fixed a typo

0.002     2013-05-30 22:42:20 America/New_York

    [ADDED]

    - experimental "--32" option to try to force 32 bit builds even on 64
      bit machines

    [CHANGED]

    - default installation directory is now set to File::Spec->tmpdir,
      not hardcoded as '/tmp'

    [FIXED]

    - exit code was accidentally inverted

0.001     2011-07-21 16:38:44 America/New_York

    - First release to CPAN

